title: The Raptors Out-Warriored the Warriors | Heat Check
description:
The Toronto Raptors push ahead to a 3-1 lead in the NBA Finals after defeating the Golden State Warriors in dominant fashion.

Host: John Gonzalez
Guests: Dan Devine, Kevin O’Connor
